title: Photograph, "Album: A & B Products"
description: Assorted canned products manufactured under the A & B label comprise the present black and white photograph. A uniform design scheme is imposed on the variously shaped cans: the A & B logo in white block serif-style type superimposed on (color in the originals) photographs of the meat products, and additional white type specifying the products.
